<h1>Plug Into the {{community_name}} Community</h1>

<div class="registration_information">
  <ul class="infolist">
    <li>The {{community_name}} CommonPlace is a safe online bulletin board for {{community_name}} residents.  It's the very best way to connect with your local community.</li>
    <li>Register once to start receiving short updates from your neighborhood, the police, the {{community_name}} city government, and great community organizations in town. <a href="{{learn_more}}" class="learn-more">LEARN MORE</a></li>
    <li>
      <div class="show-video-con">
      <h3>What Are Neighbors Saying?</h3>
      <a href="#" class="show-video"></a>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
    
</div>

<form class="new_user">
  <div class="new-top">
    <h4>Register Now</h4>
    <p class="or">or</p>
    <img class="facebook" src="/assets/facebookconnect.png">
  </div>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <input class="name" type="text" name="full_name" placeholder="Full name">
      <span class="error full_name"></span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <input class="mail" type="text" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Email address">
      <span class="error email"></span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <input class="address" type="text" name="street_address" class="has_hint" placeholder="Street address*">
      <span class="error address"></span>
      <div class="address">*This is to verify you live in {{community_name}}.  It won't be shared with anyone.</div>
      <input type="radio" id="suggested_radio" style="display:none" checked="checked" name="verify_address" value="suggested" class="address_verify_radio" /> <span style="display:none" class="address_verify_radio">Use the address we have in our system</span><br />
      <div id="suggested_address" style="display:none"></div>
      <input type="radio" style="display:none" name="verify_address" value="entered" class="address_verify_radio" /> <span style="display:none" class="address_verify_radio">Use the address I originally typed.</span><br />
      <input type="radio" id="try_again" style="display:none" name="verify_address" value="entered" class="address_verify_radio" /> <span style="display:none" class="address_verify_radio">Try typing in the address again.</span><br />
      
    </li>
  </ul>
  
  <input type="submit" class="grey-button sign_up" value="SIGN ME UP!">
</form>

<div style="clear: both;"></div>
